<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to Nadoumi Shop!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome to Nadoumi Shop!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>We are thrilled to have you on board! Thank you for joining our community.</p>
            <p>You can now explore thousands of products and enjoy a seamless shopping experience.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{year}} Nadoumi Shop. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
